'''尼爾森·C·強森'''（{{lang-en|'''Nelson C. Johnson'''}}，{{bd|1948年}}）是一名[[美國|美國]]作家、前法官、律師和歷史學家，他最著名的暢銷書是2002年的《Boardwalk Empire: The Birth, High Times and Corruption of Atlantic City》。<ref name=scotsman>{{Cite web |url = http://www.scotsman.com/lifestyle/book-review-boardwalk-empire-by-nelson-johnson-1-1494086 |title = Book review: Boardwalk Empire by Nelson Johnson |date = 2011-01-28 |publisher = The Scotsman |language = en |accessdate = 2016-04-27 |archive-date = 2015-12-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151228223245/http://www.scotsman.com/lifestyle/book-review-boardwalk-empire-by-nelson-johnson-1-1494086 |dead-url = no }}</ref>該書被改編成受歡迎兼[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]得主的[[HBO|HBO]]歷史犯罪電視劇《[[酒私風雲|酒私風雲]]》。

== 早年 ==
尼爾森·C·強森出生於1948年，並且在新澤西州[[大西洋縣|大西洋縣]]和[[紐約市|紐約市]]長大。強森是新澤西州{{link-en|哈默頓|Hammonton, New Jersey}}的長期居民。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://njmonthly.com/articles/jersey-living/atlantic-citys-godfather/ |title = Judge Nelson Johnson: Atlantic City's Godfather |author = Robert Strauss |date = 2010-08-16 |publisher = New Jersey Monthly |language = en |accessdate = 2020-05-23 |archive-date = 2020-04-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200413121138/https://njmonthly.com/articles/jersey-living/atlantic-citys-godfather/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 法律生涯 ==
1980年代期間，強森曾於[[大西洋城|大西洋城]]的規劃委員會裏工作。截至2014年，他是大西洋縣高等法院法官。<ref name=scotsman />

強森於2018年9月從新澤西州高等法院法官的職位上退休。在他擔任法官職務期間，他處理過大規模侵權案件/產品責任索賠。

== 寫作生涯 ==
強森的2002年書籍《Boardwalk Empire》被改編成[[HBO|HBO]]電視劇《[[酒私風雲|酒私風雲]]》。該書的續集是《The Northside: African Americans and the Creation of Atlantic City》。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.pressofatlanticcity.com/life/book-review-johnson-gets-it-right-with-tale-of-the/article_4d5d32bd-1107-5865-8fc1-c4665fd8e3d6.html |title = Book Review: Johnson gets it right with tale of 'The Northside' |author = Patricia Reid-Merritt |date = 2010-11-21 |publisher = Press of Atlantic City |language = en |accessdate = 2016-04-27 |archive-date = 2016-03-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304193558/http://www.pressofatlanticcity.com/life/book-review-johnson-gets-it-right-with-tale-of-the/article_4d5d32bd-1107-5865-8fc1-c4665fd8e3d6.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>2010年，他被新澤西州高等法院要求停止宣傳他自己的著作和電視劇，原因是為了維持他作為一位法官的中立立場。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://observer.com/2010/09/boardwalk-empire-author-muzzled/ |title = Boardwalk Empire Author Muzzled |author = Michael H. Miller |date = 2010-09-15 |publisher = Observer |language = en |accessdate = 2016-04-27 |archive-date = 2016-08-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160806223707/http://observer.com/2010/09/boardwalk-empire-author-muzzled/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

他的第三本書籍是《Battleground New Jersey: Vanderbilt, Hague and Their Fight for Justice》，內容講述澤西市的市長{{link-en|法蘭克·赫格|Frank Hague}}及新澤西州高等法院第一位首席法官{{link-en|阿瑟·T·范德比爾特|Arthur T. Vanderbilt}}。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.mycentraljersey.com/story/news/local/somerset-county/2015/01/16/judge-details-state-politics-history-book/21866329/ |title = Judge details state politics history in book |author = Katie Park |date = 2015-01-16 |publisher = MyCentralJersey.com |language = en |access-date = 2016-04-27 |archive-date = 2021-04-11 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411140544/https://www.mycentraljersey.com/story/news/local/somerset-county/2015/01/16/judge-details-state-politics-history-book/21866329/ }}</ref>

